<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 18pt; font-family: 標楷體;">一、檢附得獎名單乙份，恭喜獲獎學生、指導教師。</span></p>
